---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
import CTASection from "../../../components/CTASection.astro";
---

<Base title="Bequests | Homeless Hounds Animal Rescue">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-white min-h-[50vh] flex items-center">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-700 via-blue-600 to-indigo-800"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-pattern-dots opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="container-custom py-20 md:py-24 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-4">Leave a lasting legacy</p>
          <h1 class="text-white mb-6 text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold">
            Legacy <span class="text-orange-400">Bequests</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Your bequest can help save countless animals for generations to come. Create a lasting legacy that continues to make a difference.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="#information" class="btn btn-white">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
              </svg>
              Learn More
            </a>
            <a href="/contact-us" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-indigo-700 transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-indigo-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
              Get in Touch
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">

      <!-- Main Bequest Information -->
      <section id="information" class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12 scroll-mt-20">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Making a Bequest to Homeless Hounds</h3>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-6">
            A bequest is a wonderful way to ensure that your love for animals continues to make a difference
            long after you're gone. By including Homeless Hounds Animal Rescue in your will, you're helping
            to secure the future of countless animals in need.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-6">
            Every bequest, regardless of size, makes a meaningful impact. Your gift could help:
          </p>

          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Provide emergency veterinary care for rescued animals</li>
            <li>Support our foster care network with food, supplies and medical expenses</li>
            <li>Fund behavioural rehabilitation programs</li>
            <li>Expand our rescue operations to help more animals</li>
            <li>Support our volunteer training and education programs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Types of Bequests -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Types of Bequests</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

          <!-- Residuary Bequest -->
          <div class="border-l-4 border-indigo-700 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Residuary Bequest</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              A percentage or the remainder of your estate after specific gifts have been made to family and friends.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Specific Sum -->
          <div class="border-l-4 border-indigo-700 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Specific Sum</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              A fixed amount of money that you specify in your will.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Specific Assets -->
          <div class="border-l-4 border-indigo-700 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Specific Assets</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Particular items such as property, shares, or personal possessions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Life Insurance -->
          <div class="border-l-4 border-indigo-700 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Life Insurance</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Naming Homeless Hounds as a beneficiary of your life insurance policy.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Legal Requirements -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Important Legal Information</h3>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 mb-6">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
                <strong>Please seek professional legal advice</strong> when preparing or updating your will.
                A qualified solicitor can ensure your wishes are properly documented and legally binding.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-4">
            When including Homeless Hounds Animal Rescue in your will, please use our full legal name and details:
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border">
            <p class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-800 mb-2">
              <strong>Legal Name:</strong> Homeless Hounds Animal Rescue Inc.
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-800 mb-2">
              <strong>ABN:</strong> 93 136 291 221
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-800">
              <strong>Registered Address:</strong> Please contact us for current registered address details
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Sample Wording -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Sample Wording for Your Will</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Your solicitor can help you with the exact wording, but here are some examples:
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">For a specific sum:</h4>
            <p class="text-blue-800 text-sm italic">
              "I give the sum of $______ to Homeless Hounds Animal Rescue Inc. (ABN 93 136 291 221)
              for its general purposes and I direct that the receipt of the treasurer or other
              proper officer shall be sufficient discharge for my executor."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-2">For a percentage of your estate:</h4>
            <p class="text-green-800 text-sm italic">
              "I give ____% of my residuary estate to Homeless Hounds Animal Rescue Inc.
              (ABN 93 136 291 221) for its general purposes and I direct that the receipt
              of the treasurer or other proper officer shall be sufficient discharge for my executor."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">We're Here to Help</h3>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-4">
            If you're considering including Homeless Hounds in your will, or if you've already done so,
            we'd love to hear from you. While there's no obligation to tell us about your bequest,
            knowing about your intention helps us plan for the future.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6">
            We can provide additional information about our work and answer any questions you may have
            about how your bequest will be used.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-300 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-900 mb-4">Get in Touch</h4>
          <p class="text-indigo-800 mb-4">
            For more information about bequests or to discuss how your gift could make a difference:
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="/contact-us"
               class="inline-block bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-800 transition-colors text-center">
              Contact Us
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:info@homelesshounds.com.au"
               class="inline-block bg-white text-indigo-700 border-2 border-indigo-700 font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-colors text-center">
              Email Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Thank You Section -->
      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-700 to-indigo-800 rounded-lg text-white p-8 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Thank You for Considering a Bequest</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Your thoughtful gift will help ensure that future generations of animals receive the
          care, love and forever homes they deserve.
        </p>
        <p class="text-indigo-300">
          Every animal's life matters, and your legacy will help save them all.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <CTASection />
</Base>